{"metadata":{"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Property","title":"subtitle","symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"subtitle"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNAnnotation(py)subtitle","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"subtitle"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The string containing the annotation’s subtitle."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"copy"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"readonly"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"subtitle"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This string is displayed in the callout for the associated annotation."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/subtitle","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation\/subtitle"]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation/subtitle":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"subtitle","fragments":[{"text":"subtitle","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The string containing the annotation’s subtitle."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/subtitle","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation\/subtitle"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","title":"MLNAnnotation"}}}